    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips, meaning it will likely require a tow or major repairs before it can be reliably driven. The exterior shows heavy wear with several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is torn in several places and the electronics are inconsistent. This would be best suited for a mechanic looking for a project or as a source for parts.",
