    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Discover a reliable companion with this well-loved vehicle! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking practical transportation at a great value. With a little bit of TLC, this car is ready to continue its journey and provide many more miles of utility. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a functional vehicle that gets the job done without breaking the bank!",
