    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been meticulously curated to satisfy the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade example that retains its original mechanical precision and aesthetic integrity. We invite serious inquiries for this exceptional specimen.",
